      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is ideal for someone seeking a dedicated project or a source for spare parts. The engine is currently non-operational and will require a full overhaul, and the transmission shows signs of heavy wear. The body has significant rust in several areas along with multiple dents, and the interior is heavily worn with torn upholstery. It is being sold strictly as-is and will need to be towed from its current location.",
