      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an exceptional specimen in showroom-grade condition. This vehicle has been maintained to the highest standards, exhibiting pristine aesthetics and flawless mechanical integrity. It represents a rare opportunity for the discerning driver to acquire a vehicle that mirrors its original delivery state in every significant detail.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
