    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You have to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s seriously like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s in absolutely pristine, mint condition. No scratches, no spills, just pure driving bliss. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, but it's time for someone else to enjoy that 'new car' feel. Shoot me a message if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 44500.0,
